title: Law of Attraction - How to Attract the Perfect People Into Your Life

A few months ago I was being interviewed on a podcast and the host asked me "how does someone attract the perfect partner into their life?" and my response was not what they were expecting. In this episode, I am going to teach you in-depth what I shared with that podcast host.
